`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Who
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:``  

 * who
 * who <race>
 * who <clan name>
 * who pk

 Who shows the people currently in the game. Who without any arguments shows
all of the (visible) people currently playing. With arguments, Who can show
players of certain races, clans, or other defining characteristics. 

 For example: 

 * who Sendar	   lists all Sendars playing
 * who immortal    lists all immortals playing
 * who pk	   lists all visible PK characters playing

 Races may be abbreviated.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
